==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
*From [[εὖ]] {{GG|2095}} and [[ἄγγελος]] {{GG|32}}.

===Pronunciation===
*εὐαγγελίζω / euaggelizō / yoo-ang-ghel-id'-zo

===Verb===
'''εὐαγγελίζω'''

# To [[declare]], [[bring]] (declare, show) glad (good) tidings, [[preach]] (the gospel).

==Related terms==
*[[εὐαγγέλιον]]
*[[evangelize]], [[evangelise]]
*[[angel]]

